latestIgtvVideos.title: Power lies in beating the odds!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This video in collaboration with @gleamycheeks portrays how makeup in general is a misunderstood concept. On one hand women are told to “not wear too much” and men are emasculated if they choose to wear it. Both these problems root from highly sexist schools of thought!

Makeup is an ART!
And people need to understand that!!

Let people embrace themselves and do what they want to without hating on them and making them feeling unwanted!

You can disagree with us too but that doesn’t give you the right to throw slurs or try to trouble the person whose opinion doesn’t align with yours!

Show and spread love ❤️ 
Hopefully this video inspires little children yo embrace who they are whether that be through makeup,fashion etc:)

latestIgtvVideos.title: VEGAN BRIOCHE BURGER BUNS
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Super easy recipe with step by step instructions!For any queries ask me in the comments;)

Don't forget to like, share, comment and save the recipe and also tell me in the comments about what you wanna see me make next❤️

Tips:
•Use margarine(vegan butter substitute) but make sure it's vegan cause some margarines contain milk solids 
•Vital wheat gluten can easily be ordered from Amazon and you can buy it in a 500g pack and just add around a tbsp per cup of all purpose flour to improve your breads
•DO NOT use bad quality yeasts like solar, bluebird etc!
get good quality instant yeast from Amazon (it comes in a 500g pack which ik is hard to use so you can divide into portions and freeze the big portion and keep a small amount for daily/weekly/monthly use)
Gloripan yeast is available on Amazon and I use it so I'd recommend it
